			<h4>
				If your project is one 3-d print or a few-component-home-project,
				you should consider other repositories such as for example
				<a href="https://www.thingiverse.com/">thingiverse</a> or
				<a href="http://www.instructables.com/">instructables</a>.
				If you are a scientist and the data you would like to cite is not really a
				construction documentation, have a look at
				<a href="http://figshare.com/">http://figshare.com/</a>
				or alternatives.
				Perhaps you would also like to leave your project on your personal webspace or
				<a href="https://github.com/">GitHub</a>, and reference it in one of the collections below.
